<b>What?</b>

02:08.850 --> 02:10.810
<b>A pair of sleeping skulls?!</b>

02:11.360 --> 02:13.440
<b>Hah! I win.</b>

02:13.440 --> 02:14.980
<b>Don't hold it against me.</b>

02:15.530 --> 02:18.320
<b>Hey, Ryuk, wanna join us?</b>

02:18.660 --> 02:20.910
<b>Come hang out with us 
for a change.</b>

02:23.580 --> 02:26.000
<b>No, I'll pass.</b>

02:28.410 --> 02:30.880
<b>Listen for the voice of God</b>

02:30.880 --> 02:32.420
<b>and never guess you will...</b>

02:32.420 --> 02:35.800
<b>I didn't do a thing, but he still got upset...</b>

02:35.800 --> 02:36.960
<b>Really? And then?</b>

02:36.960 --> 02:39.220
<b>Yagami, what's the matter?</b>

02:39.220 --> 02:42.550
<b>Please translate the following sentences.</b>

02:46.970 --> 02:49.440
<b>Follow the voice of God.</b>

02:49.440 --> 02:52.810
<b>Then the blessings of the sea will become bountiful</b>

02:53.520 --> 02:55.530
<b>and there will be no storms.</b>

02:56.650 --> 03:00.910
<b><i>Today, at approximately 11 a.m. 
in Kanagawa Prefecture in Yokohama,</i></b>

03:00.910 --> 03:05.540
<b><i>the body of a man appearing to be about 30 years old 
was found in an apartment, covered in blood.</i></b>

03:05.540 --> 03:08.450
<b><i>Kanagawa Police have opened a homicide investigation.</i></b>

03:08.450 --> 03:09.830
<b><i>In other news...</i></b>

03:10.460 --> 03:13.750
<b><i>Today, shortly after noon, 
in the Shibuya district of Tokyo,</i></b>

03:13.750 --> 03:18.210
<b><i>a 25-year-old woman was gagged and killed by her live-in partner.</i></b>

03:18.210 --> 03:23.510
<b><i>35-year-old Tofuji Naoki is being 
held in custody charged with her murder.</i></b>

03:24.600 --> 03:26.640
<b><i>Day in and day out...</i></b>

03:27.770 --> 03:30.440
<b><i>the same thing over and over again.</i></b>

03:31.770 --> 03:33.350
<b><i>Jeez...</i></b>

03:33.350 --> 03:35.190
<b><i>It's so ridiculous.</i></b>

03:36.110 --> 03:39.650
<b><i>This world...</i></b>

03:37.650 --> 03:39.650
<b><i>...is rotten.</i></b>

03:39.650 --> 03:42.660
<b>Rebirth</b>

03:43.240 --> 03:49.450
<b>Another is the extinction of many species of life on the planet.</b>

03:47.490 --> 03:49.750
<b>No way! You went to see that?</b>

03:49.450 --> 03:54.750
<b>Species are becoming extinct 
at a faster rate than has occurred...</b>

03:49.750 --> 03:51.330
<b>It was a complete waste of time.</b>

03:51.330 --> 03:53.080
<b>I should've asked for a refund!</b>

03:53.080 --> 03:54.750
<b>Well, you <i>did</i> watch it.</b>

04:29.700 --> 04:31.160
<b><i>Death Note?</i></b>

04:31.870 --> 04:33.920
<b><i>Literally translated as "a notebook of death."</i></b>

04:37.000 --> 04:38.880
<b><i>How to use it...</i></b>

04:38.880 --> 04:42.880
<b><i>The human whose name is written in this note...</i></b>

04:42.880 --> 04:44.050
<b><i>shall die?</i></b>

04:46.470 --> 04:47.680
<b><i>What a joke...</i></b>

04:48.720 --> 04:51.640
<b><i>This is so sick.</i></b>

04:51.640 --> 04:55.980
<b><i>It's no different than a chain letter.</i></b>

04:55.980 --> 04:58.820
<b><i>"The human whose name is written in this note shall die?" C'mon.</i></b>

05:08.740 --> 05:12.040
<b><i>Seriously... I must be going insane.</i></b>

05:15.500 --> 05:19.460
<b><i>There will be no effect when the face of 
the targetted person is not in the writer's mind.</i></b>

05:19.460 --> 05:20.170
<b><i>Therefore,</i></b>

05:20.170 --> 05:24.470
<b><i>people sharing the same name will not be affected.</i></b>

05:24.470 --> 05:29.350
<b><i>If the cause of death is written within 
40 seconds of writing the person's name,</i></b>

05:29.350 --> 05:31.060
<b><i>it will happen as it is written.</i></b>

05:31.060 --> 05:34.520
<b><i>If the cause of death is not specified, 
the person will simply die of a heart attack.</i></b>

05:34.980 --> 05:37.770
<b><i>After writing the cause of death, 
in the next 6 minutes and 40 seconds,</i></b>

05:37.770 --> 05:41.270
<b><i>details of the death should be written.</i></b>

05:43.190 --> 05:46.950
<b>So you can let people die peacefully or make them suffer.</b>

05:47.280 --> 05:51.080
<b>A prank this intricate isn't too bad, I guess.</b>

05:58.040 --> 06:00.920
<b>Write their name and they die, huh?</b>

06:02.040 --> 06:03.750
<b>This is so stupid!</b>

06:19.600 --> 06:20.810
<b><i>Wait a minute.</i></b>

06:20.810 --> 06:24.280
<b><i>If someone actually dies, 
does that make me a murderer?</i></b>

06:26.320 --> 06:29.450
<b><i>No way. It'd never happen.</i></b>

06:30.240 --> 06:34.450
