06:34.450 --> 06:39.870
<b><i>has now taken eight people hostage,
 including children and teachers, in this daycare center.</i></b>

06:39.870 --> 06:44.050
<b><i>The police have now identified the suspect as 42-year-old Otoharada Kurou, unemployed.</i></b>

