06:44.460 --> 06:46.260
<b><i>The police will begin negotiations with the suspect.</i></b>

06:48.550 --> 06:50.640
<b></b>Otoharada Kurou

06:53.010 --> 06:55.060
<b><i>A heart attack in 40 seconds,</i></b>

06:55.390 --> 06:56.850
<b><i>right?</i></b>

06:58.140 --> 07:00.520
<b><i>Well, that is not clear at the moment.</i></b>

07:01.400 --> 07:04.110
<b><i>You can't help but be worried for the hostages right now.</i></b>

07:04.110 --> 07:05.270
<b><i>Absolutely.</i></b>

07:05.270 --> 07:07.820
<b><i>This has been a report from the scene.</i></b>

07:07.820 --> 07:09.320
<b><i>Thank you very much.</i></b>

07:10.030 --> 07:11.610
<b><i>What do you think, Mr. Hashimoto?</i></b>

07:11.610 --> 07:15.660
<b><i>Well, I'm hoping for a quick resolution to this.</i></b>

07:17.120 --> 07:19.540
<b><i>Oh well, nothing happened.</i></b>

07:19.540 --> 07:21.580
<b><i>What did I expect?</i></b>

07:23.250 --> 07:24.500
<b><i>Just a minute.</i></b>

07:25.090 --> 07:26.420
<b><i>There seems to be something happening.</i></b>

07:26.880 --> 07:28.130
<b><i>The hostages are coming out!</i></b>

07:28.630 --> 07:29.800
<b><i>They all seem to be fine!</i></b>

07:29.800 --> 07:32.340
<b><i>And now it looks like the SWAT team is entering!</i></b>

07:32.340 --> 07:34.010
<b><i>Has the suspect been arrested?!</i></b>

07:35.220 --> 07:36.010
<b><i>Yes!</i></b>

07:36.010 --> 07:40.270
<b><i>We just received word that the suspect has died inside the daycare center!</i></b>

07:40.770 --> 07:42.650
<b><i>The suspect is dead!</i></b>

07:42.980 --> 07:43.980
<b>Dead?!</b>

07:43.980 --> 07:46.020
<b>Otoharada</b>

07:43.980 --> 07:46.020
<b>Kurou</b>

07:46.020 --> 07:49.900
<b><i>The police are strongly denying that they shot the suspect!</i></b>

07:49.900 --> 07:53.660
<b><i>Then could he have felt cornered and committed suicide?</i></b>

07:53.660 --> 07:57.790
<b><i>According to one of the hostages, 
"The suspect just suddenly collapsed."</i></b>

07:57.790 --> 07:59.290
<b><i>A heart attack...</i></b>

08:01.910 --> 08:03.460
<b><i>N-No way...</i></b>

08:03.870 --> 08:05.380
<b><i>This is a coincidence.</i></b>

08:05.380 --> 08:07.000
<b><i>It's gotta be a coincidence!</i></b>

08:07.460 --> 08:08.630
<b>Light!</b>

08:09.710 --> 08:11.970
<b>It's almost 6:30.</b>

08:11.970 --> 08:14.260
<b>Don't you have cram school tonight?</b>

08:14.260 --> 08:16.720
<b>Yeah, I'm getting ready now.</b>

08:17.720 --> 08:18.890
<b><i>The Death Note...</i></b>

08:19.180 --> 08:22.440
<b><i>It's a long shot, but if this is the real thing,</i></b>

08:22.440 --> 08:25.310
<b><i>it's worth testing once more.</i></b>

08:26.020 --> 08:28.480
<b><i>In which case, the victim should probably be a criminal.</i></b>

08:28.980 --> 08:31.610
<b><i>But it can't be someone too infamous.</i></b>

08:31.610 --> 08:36.240
<b><i>If they die, it's possible that 
their deaths will be covered up.</i></b>

08:36.240 --> 08:38.200
<b><i>I need an immediate result.</i></b>

08:39.240 --> 08:40.580
<b>Hey, Ryo baby!</b>

08:40.580 --> 08:42.710
<b>Wh-What is it, Sudou?</b>

08:42.710 --> 08:44.670
<b>Lend me 'bout 2,000 yen, will ya?</b>

08:44.670 --> 08:46.830
<b>Wh-What? Again?</b>

08:46.830 --> 08:48.290
<b><i>Sudou...</i></b>

08:47.880 --> 08:49.250
<b>What? You refusing?</b>

08:48.290 --> 08:49.250
<b><i>Shall I kill him?</i></b>

08:50.340 --> 08:54.300
<b><i>No, I'd better avoid people I know.</i></b>

08:55.130 --> 08:55.760
<b><i>No...</i></b>

08:56.510 --> 08:59.140
<b><i>Why should I worry?</i></b>

08:59.140 --> 09:01.470
<b><i>If one or two people like him were to die,</i></b>

09:01.470 --> 09:04.310
<b><i>not a single soul would care.</i></b>

09:04.310 --> 09:07.230
<b>Now we can go to the arcade after school.</b>

09:08.190 --> 09:10.860
<b>Maki, wanna party with some guys tomorrow?</b>

09:10.860 --> 09:11.980
<b>Absolutely!</b>

09:11.980 --> 09:13.740
<b>Hey, me too!</b>

09:13.740 --> 09:15.700
<b>Dammit, that stupid old hag!</b>

09:15.700 --> 09:17.910
<b>She's not here to pick me up!</b>

09:18.990 --> 09:20.370
<b><i>It's sickening.</i></b>

09:20.370 --> 09:22.830
<b><i>Every single one of them...</i></b>

09:22.830 --> 09:26.790
<b><i>I'd do society a favor 
by killing them.</i></b>

09:28.540 --> 09:30.040
<b>Hey girl!</b>

09:31.300 --> 09:33.670
<b>Fancy having some fun with us?</b>

09:33.670 --> 09:36.550
<b>Hey, Taku! You've got a beauty there!</b>

09:37.300 --> 09:40.680
<b>I'm Shibuimaru Takuo. Shibutaku, for short.</b>

09:41.810 --> 09:44.770
<b>Hang out with us for a while, baby.</b>

09:44.770 --> 09:46.390
<b>I-I don't think so.</b>

09:46.390 --> 09:47.480
<b>She doesn't think so!</b>

09:47.480 --> 09:49.980
<b>How cute!</b>

09:54.320 --> 09:56.400
<b>C'mon, grab her. 
Get those clothes off!</b>

09:56.400 --> 09:57.990
<b>Can we?!</b>

09:59.280 --> 10:00.660
<b>Stop!</b>

10:00.660 --> 10:02.120
<b>Please!</b>

10:02.120 --> 10:04.040
<b>Stop!</b>

10:06.330 --> 10:08.960
<b>m 438 742 l 4200 742 4200 269 432 298</b>

10:06.330 --> 10:08.960
<b>tL NoTe</b>

10:06.330 --> 10:08.960
<b>|</b>

10:06.330 --> 10:08.960
<b>All the different variations of writing the name "Shibuimaru Takuo."</b>

10:08.960 --> 10:10.040
<b><i>Now let's see...</i></b>

10:10.420 --> 10:11.500
<b><i>what'll happen!</i></b>

10:14.210 --> 10:15.010
<b>Hey, wait!</b>

10:15.010 --> 10:16.090
<b>Taku! Watch out!</b>

10:23.060 --> 10:25.020
<b><i>This... This settles it!</i></b>

10:25.890 --> 10:28.560
<b><i>The Death Note is real!</i></b>

10:29.060 --> 10:30.350
<b>Taku!</b>

10:30.350 --> 10:31.770
<b>I-Idiot!</b>

10:31.770 --> 10:33.440
<b>He just jumped out in front of me.</b>

10:37.110 --> 10:38.570
<b>I guess...</b>

10:38.570 --> 10:40.990
<b>I'd better get going.</b>

10:53.750 --> 10:55.550
<b>It's been five days since then.</b>

10:56.300 --> 10:57.590
<b>I guess...</b>

10:57.590 --> 10:59.550
<b>I'd better get going.</b>

10:59.550 --> 11:02.090
<b>Huh? Going out, Ryuk?</b>

11:02.550 --> 11:05.180
<b>This place is barren everywhere you go.</b>

11:07.310 --> 11:09.480
<b>I dropped my Death Note.</b>

11:10.940 --> 11:13.400
<b>You really messed up big time!</b>

11:13.400 --> 11:17.480
<b>Hey, weren't you carrying around 
a second one behind the old man's back?</b>

11:17.480 --> 11:19.490
<b>Don't tell me you lost both of 'em?</b>

11:19.860 --> 11:22.450
<b>Do ya even know where ya dropped it?</b>

11:23.200 --> 11:24.370
<b>The Human World.</b>

11:24.370 --> 11:25.740
<b>What?!</b>

11:55.730 --> 11:56.770
<b>Welcome home.</b>

11:56.770 --> 11:59.070
<b>You're home early, Light.</b>

11:59.070 --> 11:59.940
<b>Yeah.</b>

12:00.740 --> 12:03.200
<b>I'm back, Mom.</b>

12:03.200 --> 12:03.860
<b>Huh?</b>

12:05.570 --> 12:08.540
<b>Oh, you want the results of 
the national mock entrance exams?</b>

12:08.540 --> 12:10.120
<b>Hurry!</b>

12:10.750 --> 12:12.120
<b>Here you go.</b>

12:12.120 --> 12:14.540
<b>Goodness! Number one again!</b>

12:14.540 --> 12:16.590
<b>You really did your best, Light!</b>

12:16.590 --> 12:17.840
<b>Well, yeah.</b>

12:17.840 --> 12:20.590
<b>I'll be studying, so don't bother me.</b>

12:20.590 --> 12:21.840
<b>All right.</b>

12:21.840 --> 12:23.340
<b>Oh, Light...</b>

12:23.340 --> 12:25.220
<b>Do you want anything?</b>

12:25.220 --> 12:26.890
<b>Anything at all?</b>

12:26.890 --> 12:29.100
<b>Not really, Mom.</b>

12:32.060 --> 12:34.350
<b><i>I already have what I want.</i></b>

12:53.330 --> 12:55.000
<b>You seem to like it.</b>

13:02.720 --> 13:05.300
<b>Why are you shocked?</b>

13:05.300 --> 13:09.560
<b>The one who dropped that notebook was me, Ryuk, a Shinigami.</b>

13:09.560 --> 13:11.020
<b>From what I just saw,</b>

13:11.640 --> 13:15.140
<b>you're already aware that that's no ordinary notebook.</b>

13:21.480 --> 13:22.860
<b><i>A Shinigami, huh?</i></b>

13:27.110 --> 13:29.660
<b>I'm not shocked, Ryuk.</b>

13:30.450 --> 13:31.540
<b>In fact,</b>

13:32.120 --> 13:34.660
<b>I've been waiting for you, Ryuk.</b>

13:35.210 --> 13:36.540
<b>Oh?</b>

13:36.830 --> 13:42.130
<b>I didn't think the Shinigami's Notebook was real,</b>

13:42.130 --> 13:44.260
<b>but after seeing its results,</b>

13:44.630 --> 13:47.430
<b>I can act with certainty.</b>

13:47.930 --> 13:49.760
<b>I see.</b>

13:49.760 --> 13:51.850
<b>You really surprise me.</b>

13:52.310 --> 13:58.310
<b>I've heard of Death Notes getting down 
to the Human World a few times before.</b>

13:58.850 --> 14:02.780
<b>But you're the first one to use it to this extent in just five days.</b>

14:02.780 --> 14:05.070
<b>Most people would be too scared to try it out.</b>

14:05.740 --> 14:08.110
<b>I'm prepared, Ryuk.</b>

14:08.110 --> 14:11.490
<b>I used a Death Note knowing it belonged to a Shinigami.</b>

14:11.490 --> 14:13.080
<b>And now the Shinigami's here.</b>

14:13.790 --> 14:15.330
<b>So what'll happen to me?</b>

14:15.330 --> 14:17.370
<b>Are you going to take my soul?</b>

14:17.370 --> 14:19.880
<b>Huh? What's that about?</b>

14:19.880 --> 14:22.420
<b>Some fantasy you humans came up with?</b>

14:23.340 --> 14:25.590
<b>I'm not going to do anything to you.</b>

14:26.920 --> 14:29.390
<b>Once the Death Note lands in the Human World,</b>

14:29.390 --> 14:31.720
<b>it belongs to the Human World.</b>

14:31.720 --> 14:33.600
<b>In other words,</b>

14:33.600 --> 14:35.140
<b>it belongs to you.</b>

14:35.600 --> 14:37.310
<b>It belongs to me?</b>

14:38.100 --> 14:40.900
<b>If you don't want it, give it to some other human.</b>

14:40.900 --> 14:44.980
<b>But if you do that, all memory of 
the Death Note will be erased from your mind.</b>

14:45.650 --> 14:48.900
<b>So using the Death Note</b>

14:48.900 --> 14:50.240
<b>doesn't come with a catch?</b>

14:50.780 --> 14:52.660
<b>Well, if anything, there is...</b>

14:52.660 --> 14:56.790
<b>only the fear and pain humans who 
have used the Death Note will experience.</b>

14:58.290 --> 15:00.330
<b>And when you die,</b>

15:00.670 --> 15:05.130
<b>it falls to me to write your name in my Death Note.</b>

15:06.090 --> 15:08.590
<b>Don't think for a moment, that any human</b>

15:08.590 --> 15:11.720
<b>who's used the Death Note can go to Heaven, or Hell.</b>

15:13.140 --> 15:14.390
<b>That's all.</b>

15:19.230 --> 15:21.770
<b>You'll find out about it after you die.</b>

15:25.690 --> 15:27.030
<b>Light...</b>

15:27.030 --> 15:28.320
<b>Don't worry.</b>

15:28.320 --> 15:29.320
<b>Answer her.</b>

15:32.110 --> 15:32.910
<b>What?</b>

15:32.910 --> 15:34.700
<b>I brought some apples.</b>

15:34.700 --> 15:36.830
<b>They're from our neighbors.</b>

15:36.830 --> 15:39.000
<b>Why is it so dark in there?</b>

15:39.290 --> 15:41.040
<b>You'll ruin your eyesight!</b>

15:40.580 --> 15:41.710
<b><i>What's going on?</i></b>

15:41.040 --> 15:41.710
<b>Geez.</b>

15:42.210 --> 15:44.500
<b><i>Mom can't see him?</i></b>

15:45.790 --> 15:49.800
<b>That notebook originally 
belonged to me.</b>

15:49.800 --> 15:52.510
<b>And since you're the one using it,</b>

15:52.510 --> 15:55.140
<b>only you can see me.</b>

15:55.140 --> 15:56.350
<b>Of course, my voice...</b>

15:56.350 --> 15:58.180
<b>Only you can hear it.</b>

15:58.180 --> 15:59.390
<b>In other words, the Death Note</b>

15:59.890 --> 16:03.020
<b>is a bond between Light the human and Ryuk the Shinigami.</b>

16:07.270 --> 16:08.030
<b>Tasty.</b>

16:08.480 --> 16:10.280
<b>Let me ask you one more thing.</b>

16:10.990 --> 16:12.990
<b>Why did you choose me?</b>

16:14.070 --> 16:15.450
<b>Hey, are you listening?</b>

16:18.700 --> 16:21.790
<b>Apples in the Human World are awesome.</b>

16:21.790 --> 16:23.420
<b>What would you call them?</b>

16:24.040 --> 16:24.670
<b>Juicy?</b>

16:24.670 --> 16:26.250
<b>Answer my question.</b>

16:27.420 --> 16:29.050
<b>I didn't choose you.</b>

16:29.050 --> 16:31.880
<b>I just dropped the notebook.</b>

16:31.880 --> 16:35.010
<b>Did you think you were chosen because you were smart?</b>

16:35.010 --> 16:36.050
<b>Don't flatter yourself.</b>

16:37.260 --> 16:40.720
<b>It just happened to fall around here and you just happened to pick it up.</b>

16:40.720 --> 16:42.430
<b>That's all.</b>

16:43.060 --> 16:47.400
<b>That's why I wrote the explanation in English, 
the most popular language in the Human World.</b>

16:47.690 --> 16:49.650
<b>Then why did you drop it?!</b>

16:49.650 --> 16:53.950
<b>Don't tell me it was by mistake after you went to the trouble and wrote all those instructions.</b>

16:54.610 --> 16:56.110
<b>Why'd I drop it?</b>

16:56.870 --> 16:58.950
<b>Because I was bored.</b>

17:00.040 --> 17:01.450
<b>Bored?</b>

17:03.040 --> 17:06.120
<b>The truth is that Shinigami these days have a lot of time on their hands.</b>

17:06.120 --> 17:08.960
<b>They're either taking a nap or gambling.</b>

17:09.960 --> 17:12.760
<b>If others see you studiously scribbling names in the Death Note,</b>

17:12.760 --> 17:15.470
<b>they'll say, "What are you working so hard for?" and laugh at you.</b>

17:16.300 --> 17:19.720
<b>Writing names of other Shinigami doesn't work.</b>

17:19.720 --> 17:22.140
<b>But since we live in the Shinigami Realm,</b>

17:22.140 --> 17:25.980
<b>it's no fun at all to kill people who live in the Human World!</b>

17:27.270 --> 17:31.190
<b>So I figured it'd be more fun to come down here myself.</b>

17:32.820 --> 17:36.280
<b>But you sure wrote a lotta names.</b>

17:36.280 --> 17:40.780
<b>But why'd you write down the cause of death only for that guy who was hit by the truck?</b>

17:41.160 --> 17:44.750
<b>Without the cause of death written down, 
they all die of heart attacks.</b>

17:44.750 --> 17:48.040
<b>That's the best thing about the Death Note, Ryuk.</b>

17:49.840 --> 17:53.260
<b>I can write down the names of the criminals</b>

17:53.260 --> 17:55.630
<b>and slowly reduce the number of evil people.</b>

17:55.630 --> 17:57.430
<b>What's the point?</b>

17:57.800 --> 18:02.430
<b>Any fool can figure it out if someone is just "eliminating the bad guys."</b>

18:03.020 --> 18:06.020
<b>I want the world to know of my existence!</b>

18:06.600 --> 18:09.400
<b>That there is someone passing judgment on them!</b>

18:11.730 --> 18:16.280
<b>But what's the point in passing judgment?</b>

18:16.280 --> 18:17.570
<b>Why do it?</b>

18:18.740 --> 18:20.410
<b>I, too,</b>

18:20.410 --> 18:22.120
<b>was bored.</b>

18:24.700 --> 18:27.040
<b>Naturally, I didn't believe it at first.</b>

18:27.040 --> 18:28.790
<b>But that Death Note</b>

18:28.790 --> 18:33.090
<b>has the supernatural power to tempt people 
to want to try it at least once.</b>

18:34.630 --> 18:37.090
<b><i>I... I killed them.</i></b>

18:37.670 --> 18:38.930
<b><i>Two men...</i></b>

18:39.510 --> 18:41.350
<b><i>I killed them!</i></b>

18:42.800 --> 18:44.220
<b><i>Human lives...</i></b>

18:44.220 --> 18:46.310
<b><i>shouldn't be taken so lightly!</i></b>

18:46.310 --> 18:49.850
<b><i>Do I have the right 
to judge people like that?</i></b>

18:52.060 --> 18:53.230
<b><i>No...</i></b>

18:53.230 --> 18:54.860
<b><i>I'm not wrong!</i></b>

18:54.860 --> 18:57.070
<b><i>I've always thought about this.</i></b>

18:57.070 --> 18:58.740
<b><i>The world is rotten!</i></b>

18:59.240 --> 19:01.740
<b><i>Rotten people deserve to die!</i></b>

19:02.410 --> 19:03.580
<b><i>Someone...</i></b>

19:03.580 --> 19:06.500
<b><i>Someone has to do it!</i></b>

19:06.500 --> 19:10.040
<b><i>Even if it means sacrificing 
one's conscience and life!</i></b>

19:10.040 --> 19:13.250
<b><i>Things can't stay like this!</i></b>

19:13.920 --> 19:17.090
<b><i>If the Death Note had fallen into someone else's hands,</i></b>

19:17.550 --> 19:21.180
<b><i>would they have had the resolve 
to erase unwanted people from this world?</i></b>

19:21.180 --> 19:23.100
<b><i>No way!</i></b>

19:23.100 --> 19:24.930
<b><i>But I...</i></b>

19:24.970 --> 19:26.310
<b><i>I can do it!</i></b>

19:27.600 --> 19:28.930
<b><i>In fact,</i></b>

19:28.930 --> 19:31.230
<b><i>only I can do it!</i></b>

19:31.230 --> 19:33.810
<b><i>And I will! With the Death Note!</i></b>

19:34.980 --> 19:36.780
<b><i>I'll change the world!</i></b>

20:14.270 --> 20:16.570
<b>At first I kept writing the names of criminals</b>

20:16.570 --> 20:19.230
<b>as if I were cleaning up the world.</b>

20:19.230 --> 20:23.320
<b>So that in time, no one would do evil.</b>

20:23.570 --> 20:28.540
<b>While those guilty ones who truly deserved to be punished for their crimes die of heart attacks,</b>

20:28.540 --> 20:32.160
<b>people who were immoral or harass others,</b>

20:32.160 --> 20:35.420
<b>would slowly be erased through illness or accidents.</b>

20:35.420 --> 20:39.840
<b>Then the world would truly move in the right direction.</b>

20:40.420 --> 20:46.850
<b>And I would create a new world of earnest, kind humans.</b>

20:47.300 --> 20:51.060
<b>Then you'd be the only 
fucked-up person left.</b>

20:51.060 --> 20:53.560
<b>Huh? What are you saying?</b>

20:53.560 --> 20:54.520
<b>Ryuk,</b>

20:54.980 --> 20:59.400
<b>I'm probably the best, most diligent honor student in Japan.</b>

21:01.530 --> 21:03.280
<b>And I will become...</b>

21:05.320 --> 21:07.570
<b>the god of the new world!</b>

21:09.910 --> 21:12.120
<b><i>I knew it! Humans...</i></b>

21:13.290 --> 21:14.960
<b><i>sure are interesting.</i></b>

21:23.050 --> 21:26.090
<b>To be continued</b>

